"Overall:  Wow!  What an incredibly unique and delicious beer!  I love the beautiful balanced flavors of sweet, toasted malt and peat.  This is a Scotch-lover’s Scotch Ale!!  Between this and the Slingshot, I’m impressed with this brewery!  Thanks to my brother for bringing them back with him from Iowa after visiting his in-laws!"
"Very easy to drink, brown color."
